data.description: Spacious 4-bedroom home in Center Grove!!! NO HOA!!! Enjoy your new home with a covered front porch featuring 2 swings and beautiful landscaping.  Newly refinished cabinets and countertops in the kitchen with osmosis filter, brand new rangehood, microwave and double oven. New waterproof LVP flooring throughout within the last 2 years. In the living room you will find a gas fireplace, along with a wood burning fireplace in the spacious tiled sunroom. Right off of the sunroom you will find a large deck in the backyard with plenty of trees for privacy. The garage features plenty of storage space and a workspace for the handiest of people.
